Summary: Just taking pictures of the stars!
divs: Sighting DetailsAs I was taking pictures of the stars as I do may times on clear nights, I came across some U.F.O.'s Thus I can not identify the objects. They were not planes or rain drops, Dew, or bugs. I have asked questions as to what they may be and NO one can answer the question. SO they are U.F.O.'s I did not see the objects until I placed them on the Computer to look at. The Camera that took these was a Canon PowerShot SX30IS at X145, and at x35...
